  "rp_sheet": {
    "bio": "Kyra Callaghan of Highridge \u2014 a Taraf-Imro Human champion, fire-touched and proud of it. Mountain forges raised her; the Fivefold Flame claimed her. She carries a forearm scar earned in her first real fight and displays it half-hidden, half-shown. She is used to winning and unbothered by the rare times she hasn't.",
    "personality": "Confident to the edge of arrogance. Quick smile, certain of outcomes. Runs hot in every sense. Respects challenge, disdains cowardice, laughs with her whole body.",
    "goals": [
      "Earn her name beyond the Highridge forges \u2014 be known across Oreka.",
      "Master the Fivefold Flame's fire without being consumed by it.",
      "Find opponents who actually push her."
    ],
    "quirks": [
      "Sparks answer her when she flexes her fingers. She doesn't hide it.",
      "A subtle, constant heat lingers in the air around her.",
      "Arrives in rooms rather than enters them \u2014 shoulders back, chin high."
    ],
